<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>HYMN OF LAUDS FROM EASTER TO ASCENSION</B></FONT></H2>
<H3><PRE>

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                 G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. From the abyss of death
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Christ ascends victorious
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     F                         E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   together with the ancient fathers.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                  G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. Shines the sun of Easter,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                           Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   resounds the sky with songs,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">       F             E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   rejoices all the earth.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                 G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. From the abyss of death
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Christ ascends victorious
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     F                         E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   together with the ancient fathers.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. Beside the empty tomb
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in vain the guardian watches:
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   the Lord is risen!

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                 G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. From the abyss of death
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Christ ascends victorious
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     F                         E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   together with the ancient fathers.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. O Jesus, immortal King,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   join to your victory
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   those reborn in baptism.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                 G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. From the abyss of death
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Christ ascends victorious
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     F                         E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   together with the ancient fathers.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. May the light of your Easter,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   pledge of love and peace,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   shine upon your Church.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                 G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. From the abyss of death
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Christ ascends victorious
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     F                         E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   together with the ancient fathers.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C+A. Glory and honor to Christ,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     to the Father and the Holy Spirit
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     now and forever.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     Am    G     Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Amen! Amen! Amen!

